        static OrderUpdater from(int id,
                         int customer,

                         int slope,
                         boolean active,
                         ShedUpdater shedUpdater,
                         java.lang.String comment)
        Returns a new order updater from the provided information.
        Parameters:
        id - The id of the order to update.
        customer - The customer of the order to specify in the updater.
        width - The width of the order to specify in the updater.
        length - The length of the order to specify in the updater.
        height - The height of the order to specify in the updater.
        roofing - The roofing of the order to specify in the updater.
        slope - The slope of the order to specify in the updater.
        active - The active status of the order in the updater.
        shedUpdater - The shed to include in the order. null when the order has no shed.
        comment - The comment by the customer about the order.
        Returns:
        The newly created order updater.
